description: Drone manufacturer/model database for nozyme enrichment. Covers consumer, prosumer, enterprise, FPV, agricultural, delivery, industrial, survey, and public-safety drones. OUI database includes IEEE-confirmed manufacturer blocks, observed product OUIs, and Espressif ESP32 module OUIs for FPV/DIY drone detection.
